latestIgtvVideos.title: ☀️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello, I'm Musskan, the creative head of my brand 'Kiwi by Musskan'. I started this journey around 10 years ago with the vision to enhance the aura of  people by simply wearing a piece of jewellery. 
No matter how you've styled your outfit but wearing kiwi always steals the show. I use precious n semi-precious stones and curate it with pearls, jute n other gems. Some of my designs can be styled in different ways to give it a fresh look everytime you wear them. 
Since childhood I admired my grandmother,mother and other women adorned in classic pieces made of precious stones n I always dreamt of creating exclusive designs of my own. So here I'm living my dream... Support my small business ,we are standing tall is all cause of you all .
